INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('21571914-973c-4210-ab68-5dd8ae9fc09f', '6bc7b47e-4179-4cf2-a5bb-c4ea090ef297', 'en-US', 'Leather Bracelet', 'The fashionable leather bracelet collection combines soft materials with metal embellishments, showcasing a casual and cool style. It adds a touch of unrestrained charm to your wrist, making it an ideal accessory for those who seek leisure and personal expression, suitable for various occasions.', 'Leather Bracelet - A Casual and Cool Personalized Wrist Accessory', 'Discover our fashionable leather bracelet collection, combining soft, high-quality leather with metal embellishments. Our leather bracelets come in a variety of colors, widths, and buckle designs, showcasing a casual yet edgy style. The leather is specially treated to ensure durability and a comfortable wearing experience. Metal details such as pendants, chains, and studs add striking accents, enhancing the overall design. These leather bracelets are perfect for those who embrace a laid-back style and seek to express their individuality, adding a touch of unrestrained charm to the wrist. Whether paired with jeans, casual shirts, or stylish jackets, they help display a unique personal style. We offer options for both men and women, with each piece meticulously crafted to ensure quality and texture. They make ideal accessories for daily wear and self-expression, reflecting a free-spirited and adventurous lifestyle.', 'Leather Bracelet, Cool Accessories, Casual Style, Personal Expression', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('6eb54f02-17ef-42bb-8118-927590b79d04', '62ce3ff8-fe78-4775-80c4-9ab23844def4', 'en-US', 'Metal Series', 'The metal-themed jewelry series highlights the texture and luster of the metal itself, showcasing strength and modern aesthetics through forging, carving, and other crafts. It offers wearers a style choice that combines toughness with elegance, becoming a representative of avant-garde fashion and classic design.', 'Metal Jewelry - Modern Power with Textured Luster', 'Explore our metal-themed jewelry collection, which highlights the texture and luster of the metal itself. Our metal jewelry includes a variety of materials such as sterling silver, gold, rose gold, and titanium steel, showcasing strength and modern aesthetics through techniques like forging, carving, and polishing. Designs range from minimalist geometry to intricate sculptural styles, appealing to those who seek avant-garde fashion and classic elegance. Metal jewelry embodies a style that combines toughness with grace, becoming a focal point in any ensemble. Each piece is meticulously crafted to ensure metal purity and quality of craftsmanship. Whether for everyday wear or special occasions, metal jewelry expresses a unique fashion attitude, conveys modern aesthetics and individuality, and serves as both a timeless classic and an edgy choice for jewelry collectors, remaining forever stylish and eye-catching.', 'Metal jewelry, textured luster, modern design, powerful beauty', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('0ccd2653-0421-4a42-a667-0ea46a04429b', 'c2602244-50d1-43f0-b2a5-5929baa487e0', 'en-US', 'Tibetan-style products', 'Explore a rich variety of traditional Tibetan items, from exquisite Tibetan jewelry to sacred practice tools. Each piece is imbued with deep cultural significance and spiritual value, offering you a glimpse into the unique charm of the high plateau.', 'Tibetan Style Products - A Perfect Blend of Tradition and Spirituality', 'Discover our extensive collection of traditional Tibetan items, ranging from exquisite Tibetan jewelry to sacred practice tools. Each piece is rich in cultural significance and spiritual value. Our Tibetan products are carefully selected to ensure high-quality materials and exquisite craftsmanship, showcasing the unique charm of the snow-covered plateau. Whether for personal practice, home decoration, or as a precious gift, these items offer a unique cultural experience and spiritual inspiration, bridging ancient wisdom with modern life and serving as an ideal window into Tibetan culture.', 'Tibetan goods, Tibetan jewelry, practice tools, Tibetan culture', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('95ef5af1-ac9e-4cc1-b499-becf33b618d5', 'a80a2ae9-814d-4577-8f23-ea959c891462', 'en-US', 'Tibetan-style bracelet', 'The exquisite Tibetan-style bracelet series, crafted with traditional techniques and natural materials, displays a unique ethnic style and mysterious charm, making it an ideal accessory for expressing individuality and cultural identity.', 'Tibetan-style Bracelet - The Mysterious Charm of Ethnic Style', 'Discover our exquisite collection of Tibetan-style bracelets, crafted with traditional techniques and natural materials. These bracelets incorporate unique design elements of the Tibetan culture, such as colorful bead strands, metal engravings, and Buddha patterns, showcasing a rich ethnic style and mysterious allure. Each piece is meticulously handcrafted by experienced artisans to ensure exceptional detail and quality. A Tibetan-style bracelet is not just a fashion accessory but also carries the beliefs and blessings of the Tibetan people. It''s perfect for everyday wear, cultural events, or as a gift, making it an ideal choice for expressing individuality and cultural identity while adding a unique exotic touch to your outfit.', 'Tibetan-style bracelet, ethnic jewelry, traditional craftsmanship, Buddha image pattern', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('54ad3fdd-ca8e-4fb2-8580-1f7bd2abfa1a', '10df813e-1b02-49d5-8389-0915c992c53c', 'en-US', 'Tibetan Prayer Beads & Necklaces', 'The Tibetan Prayer Beads and Necklace collection integrates religious elements with fashion design, suitable for both spiritual practice and daily wear. It perfectly blends spiritual beliefs with aesthetic styles, serving as a bridge connecting the inner self with culture.', 'Tibetan Prayer Beads & Necklaces - A Combination of Faith and Fashion', 'Explore our Tibetan prayer beads and necklace collection, blending religious elements with fashionable designs. Our prayer beads are crafted from high-quality materials such as wood, gemstones, and coral, with traditional bead counts like 108 or 21, perfect for spiritual practice and meditation. The necklaces incorporate elements like Buddha images, scriptures, and talismans, featuring styles ranging from traditional to modern minimalist. These accessories serve not only as spiritual tools but also as stylish ornaments, reflecting the wearer''s beliefs and aesthetic taste. Each piece is blessed by monks and imbued with energy to ensure its sanctity and cultural value. Ideal for religious ceremonies, everyday wear, or as cherished gifts, they help connect you with inner peace and Tibetan culture, symbolizing both spiritual practice and fashion expression.', 'Tibetan prayer beads, bead necklace, practice tool, religious jewelry', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('1567a206-17f7-4f19-8c28-91103454a146', 'c5f96dac-d07a-4a7f-91ad-28e06c216215', 'en-US', 'Tibetan-style rings', 'Unique Tibetan-style ring series, showcasing individuality with bold designs and symbolic elements. Crafted with metal and gemstones, it integrates traditional craftsmanship with modern aesthetics, becoming a cultural expression and symbol of strength between the fingers.', 'Tibetan Ring - A Bold Design Cultural Symbol', 'Discover our unique Tibetan-style ring collection, where bold designs and symbolic motifs express individuality. Crafted from premium metals such as silver, gold, and copper, these rings are inlaid with precious materials like gemstones, coral, and turquoise, showcasing traditional Tibetan patterns including the Eight Auspicious Symbols, the Six Syllables Mantra, and Buddha images. Each ring undergoes meticulous carving and hand polishing to ensure comfort and exceptional quality. Beyond being fashion accessories, Tibetan-style rings carry symbolic meanings of blessings, protection, and wisdom, making them suitable for any occasion as a cultural expression and symbol of strength. Whether you''re seeking a distinctive style or cultural heritage, these rings will add unique charm to your look while conveying profound spiritual significance.', 'Tibetan ring, symbolic motifs, traditional patterns, metal gemstones', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('6294daff-8537-40db-8719-de399776c807', '4aeb9171-2dce-486e-b586-9f7536c8e889', 'en-US', 'Tibetan Singing Bowl', 'Traditional Tibetan singing bowl series, crafted from bronze alloy, producing harmonious vibrations when struck, used for meditation, healing, and ceremonies. They help balance energy and create a sacred atmosphere, making them ideal tools for sound healing.', 'Tibetan Singing Bowl - A meditation tool for harmonic vibration', 'Explore our traditional Tibetan singing bowl collection, crafted with meticulous care from bronze alloy. These singing bowls produce deep, harmonious vibrations through striking or rubbing, each with unique frequencies used for meditation, sound healing, energy cleansing, and various spiritual practices. Tibetan singing bowls hold significant importance in Buddhist rituals, aiding practitioners in focusing their attention, balancing mind-body energy, and achieving deep meditative states. Our singing bowls are carefully selected to ensure pure tone quality and long-lasting vibrations. Each bowl comes with a dedicated wooden mallet and usage guide, making it suitable for both beginners and professionals. Whether for personal practice, healing workshops, or maintaining home energy balance, Tibetan singing bowls can create a sacred atmosphere, bringing harmony to body and mind, as well as inner peace, becoming a valuable tool in the field of sound healing.', 'Tibetan singing bowl, sound healing, meditation tool, energy balance', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('c1cbf54f-5feb-444b-84c0-9acbff0ac456', 'f39d7472-164b-4860-b4c7-51e0b00684cb', 'en-US', 'Tibetan Prayer Flags', 'Tibetan prayer flag series in colorful designs, printed with scriptures and auspicious patterns. As they flutter in the wind, they spread blessings and positive energy. Used for decoration and making wishes, they add a sacred atmosphere and cultural beauty to the environment.', 'Tibetan Prayer Flags - Auspicious Blessings Spread by the Wind', 'Explore our vibrant Tibetan prayer flag series, printed with traditional scriptures and auspicious patterns. Made from high-quality fabric, these prayer flags feature long-lasting colors and designs including Buddhist scriptures, Buddha images, divine beasts, and more, symbolizing blessings, protection, and the spread of positive energy. In Tibetan culture, prayer flags represent sacred prayers, and as they flutter in the wind, they are believed to spread spiritual messages and blessings. We offer a variety of sizes and lengths, perfect for home decoration, garden arrangement, travel souvenirs, or religious ceremonies. Hanging prayer flags not only enhances the environment with a sacred atmosphere and cultural beauty but also serves as a way to participate in Tibetan spiritual practices, bringing harmony and peace to living spaces while conveying wishes and blessings.', 'Tibetan prayer flags, scripture patterns, auspicious blessings, home decoration', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('ed6db946-ec19-4c07-91d1-f75ed6468558', '8093514d-3e58-45cc-812f-1c4b04f9c904', 'en-US', 'Tibetan Prayer Wheel', 'Tibetan prayer wheel series, containing scriptures inside, accumulating merit through rotation, used for personal cultivation and blessings, showcasing exquisite craftsmanship and profound religious significance, and is an important ritual object in Tibetan Buddhism.', 'Tibetan Prayer Wheel - A Ritual Object for Accumulating Merit by Rotation', 'Explore our Tibetan prayer wheel collection, each containing a vast number of scriptures. By turning the wheel, you can accumulate merit and blessings. Our prayer wheels are crafted from high-quality materials such as wood, metal, and leather, with designs ranging from small handheld sizes to large courtyard decorations. Every prayer wheel is consecrated by monks to ensure its religious significance and spiritual value. In Tibetan Buddhism, the prayer wheel symbolizes the spread of the Dharma and the practice of spiritual cultivation. One rotation of the wheel is equivalent to reciting all the scriptures contained within. These ritual objects are perfect for personal practice, home decoration, temple offerings, or as precious gifts. Whether used for personal chanting or as a courtyard display, the prayer wheel can bring a sacred atmosphere to your living space, serving as a bridge between the material world and the spiritual realm, conveying endless blessings and wisdom.', 'Tibetan prayer wheel, scripture instrument, merit accumulation, religious significance', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('d863c2dd-1a56-4f1a-8b28-d7e89f751981', 'f7ff8396-f88d-49db-b1f2-dc6fad6fe96f', 'en-US', 'Tibetan bells', 'Traditional Tibetan bronze bell series, crafted from pure copper, producing a crisp sound for meditation and ceremonies, symbolizing the combination of wisdom and compassion, helping to focus the mind and create a sacred and solemn atmosphere.', 'Tibetan Copper Bell - Aids in Practice with Crisp Sounds', 'Discover our traditional Tibetan copper bell collection, crafted with pure copper. These bells are intricately designed, often featuring dragons and other auspicious symbols, and produce a crisp, resonant sound suitable for meditation, prayer, rituals, and various spiritual practices. In Tibetan Buddhism, the copper bell symbolizes the perfect union of wisdom (emptiness) and compassion (method), helping practitioners focus, purify spaces, and dispel distractions. Our bells come in multiple sizes and sound options, ideal for personal practice, temple ceremonies, or home energy cleansing. Each bell is finely tuned to ensure pure tone and long-distance sound projection. Using these bells not only enhances your practice but also connects ancient wisdom with modern spiritual traditions, adding traditional strength and cultural depth to your spiritual journey.', 'Tibetan bronze bell, practice auxiliary, wisdom and compassion, ritual instrument', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813', '2025-06-11 05:22:05.050813');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('ac3381a0-ad27-448b-ad39-df09711e6dec', '2445fe19-b637-4d6c-898d-4824651278f6', 'en-US', 'Thangka', 'The traditional Thangka painting series, featuring Buddhist figures and Tibetan myths created with mineral pigments, displays exquisite painting skills and profound spiritual connotations. It is a treasure of Tibetan art, with both collection and decorative value.', 'Thangka Painting - The Spiritual Treasure of Tibetan Art', 'Explore our traditional Thangka painting collection, featuring intricate depictions of Buddhas and Tibetan mythological scenes crafted with mineral pigments. Our Thangkas are handmade by experienced artists who follow time-honored techniques passed down for thousands of years, utilizing precious materials such as gold foil, silver foil, and gemstone powders to ensure vibrant colors and fine, fluid lines. Each Thangka carries deep religious significance and spiritual value, portraying the sacred images of Buddhas and Bodhisattvas along with the Tibetan cosmological perspective. More than just artworks, Thangkas serve as aids for meditation and visualization practices. We offer a variety of sizes and themes, including Buddhas, Bodhisattvas, Dharma protectors, and Yidams, suitable for home altars, temple decorations, or art collections. Every piece comes with detailed background information and care instructions, helping you appreciate its cultural depth and preserve this artistic treasure from the snowy plateau, bringing sanctity and cultural richness to your living space.', 'Thangka painting, Tibetan art, Buddha thangka, art collection', '2025-06-11 05:24:12.404358', '2025-06-11 05:24:12.404358');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('60324ecb-c016-4a2a-8bdb-dd49da181e9b', 'a10e684e-553f-4200-9f07-311dbead4a88', 'en-US', 'Tibetan Heavenly Beads', 'The precious Tibetan celestial bead series, crafted from natural stones and mysterious techniques, carries ancient legends and protective energy, displaying unique textures and mystical charm, making it an ideal choice for collection and wearing.', 'Tibetan Sky Pearl - Protective Gemstone with Mysterious Patterns', 'Discover our exquisite Tibetan Sky Pearl collection, crafted from natural stones using ancient and mysterious techniques. Sky Pearls are renowned for their unique textures, eye patterns, and designs, each pattern carrying specific spiritual significance and protective qualities. In Tibetan culture, Sky Pearls are considered auspicious talismans that can ward off evil, bring good luck, and enhance energy. Our Sky Pearls undergo rigorous authentication to ensure their authenticity and quality, available in various styles such as single beads, bracelets, and necklaces. Sky Pearls are perfect for collecting, wearing, or gifting as a precious present; their mysterious charm and cultural value make them an ideal choice for jewelry enthusiasts and cultural explorers. Each Sky Pearl comes with detailed pattern explanations and care instructions, helping you deeply understand its essence and experience the modern inheritance of ancient wisdom.', 'Tibetan celestial beads, protective gemstones, mysterious patterns, cultural heritage', '2025-06-11 05:24:12.404358', '2025-06-11 05:24:12.404358');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('5184b67e-738b-476d-b3b4-3c7ca3adff18', '2ffc2508-b703-4831-9c0b-f96b5c5539dd', 'en-US', 'Tibetan Clothing & Scarves', 'The Tibetan traditional clothing and scarf collection, made from thick fabric and vibrant colors, showcases ethnic style, providing warmth and comfort. It''s the ideal attire for experiencing Tibetan life, suitable for travel and special occasions.', 'Tibetan Clothing & Scarves - A Warm Choice with Ethnic Charm', 'Explore our collection of traditional Tibetan clothing and scarves, crafted from substantial materials such as wool, yak down, and cotton. These vibrant pieces feature patterns rich in ethnic charm. Our clothing range includes Tibetan robes, shirts, hats, and more, while our scarves come in various sizes and wearing styles, showcasing the unique aesthetics and cultural characteristics of Tibet. Not only are these garments stylish and elegant, but they also offer excellent warmth and comfort, making them ideal for high-altitude climates and outdoor activities. By wearing Tibetan clothing and scarves, you can immerse yourself in the Tibetan way of life and become part of its cultural heritage. Our products are perfect for travelers, participants in cultural events, or anyone seeking a distinctive style, adding an exotic allure to everyday attire and serving as a fashionable bridge between tradition and modernity.', 'Tibetan clothing, ethnic costumes, warm scarves, traditional style', '2025-06-11 05:24:12.404358', '2025-06-11 05:24:12.404358');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('85a4d3da-3ca9-48e1-b388-590e803faeda', '4d78477c-c274-42c5-8838-9d9a8cb206e2', 'en-US', 'Tibetan Conch', 'The Tibetan Conch Series, as an important Buddhist ritual instrument, is used in ceremonies and meditation. Its sound symbolizes the spread of Buddhist teachings, helping to purify the space and enhance the practice atmosphere, showcasing its sacred cultural significance and practical value.', 'Tibetan Conch - A Sacred Ritual Object for Spreading Dharma Sounds', 'Explore our Tibetan Conch series, one of the essential ritual instruments in Buddhism. These conches are carefully polished from natural large shells, producing a resonant sound when blown, which is believed to purify space, dispel evil, and spread the Dharma. In Tibetan Buddhism, the conch symbolizes the spreading of Buddha''s teachings and the sound of victory, often used in religious ceremonies, meditation guidance, and prayer activities. Our conches come in various sizes and decoration options, ranging from simple natural styles to elaborate designs with gemstone inlays and metal carvings. Each conch includes a user guide and cultural background information to ensure its proper use and understanding of its significance. Whether for personal practice, temple rituals, or home energy purification, Tibetan conches can add a sacred atmosphere to your spiritual practice, serving as a precious bridge connecting ancient wisdom with modern practice, conveying the power of peace and awakening.', 'Tibetan conch, ritual conch, space purification, spread of Buddhism', '2025-06-11 05:24:12.404358', '2025-06-11 05:24:12.404358');
