INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('1c9a7a85-349a-4c26-a9fc-0db96785d1e2', '09c86466-821a-44b2-9210-36a618d08a78', 'en-US', 'Blankets', 'The Comfort Blanket Series, made from thick materials such as wool, cotton, and linen, is suitable for various purposes including meditation mats, yoga towels, and home decorations, providing warm and comfortable support for mind-body practices and daily relaxation.', 'Cozy Blankets - A Warm and Practical Home Choice', 'The Comfort Blanket Series is crafted from thick, warm materials such as wool, cotton, and linen. Our blankets are versatile, suitable for various uses including meditation mats, yoga towels, sofa throws, and bed blankets, providing warmth and comfort for both your mind-body practices and daily relaxation. The fabrics undergo special treatment to ensure softness, breathability, and durability, with some styles also featuring health benefits like antibacterial and anti-mite properties. The design styles range from minimalist solids to ethnic patterns and geometric textures, catering to different home decor styles. Each blanket is meticulously woven and quality-checked to ensure dimensional stability, colorfastness, and excellent texture. Whether used as a meditation aid, yoga practice towel, or home decor item, our blankets offer all-around comfort and become a warm companion in your life.', 'Cozy blanket, thick fabric, meditation mat, home decor', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('791a5d08-4361-47da-8fe1-a9501b6c3d32', '1bc893b2-5227-4cd2-871d-10cdf3b89da4', 'en-US', 'Home Decor Accessories', 'Home Decor Accessories', 'Home Decor Accessories', 'Home Decor Accessories', 'Home Decor Accessories', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('dc39c2b7-4235-410b-bb35-102af25e1b56', '0fb693d4-66d7-4633-9d09-1473c3038f6e', 'en-US', 'Buddha Statues', 'An exquisite series of Buddha statues, including depictions of Shakyamuni Buddha, Laughing Buddha, Guanyin Bodhisattva, Ganesha, and more. Crafted from premium materials, these statues embody dignity and compassion, creating a sacred atmosphere for your spiritual practice and home decor.', 'Buddha Statues Series - A Spiritual Symbol of Dignity and Compassion', 'An exquisite series of Buddha statues, including depictions of Shakyamuni Buddha, Laughing Buddha, Guanyin Bodhisattva, Ganesha, and more. Our Buddha statues are crafted from premium materials such as brass, black sandalwood, crystal, and resin. Each statue undergoes meticulous carving and fine polishing to reveal expressions of solemnity and compassion. The Buddha statues serve not only as focal points for meditation and spiritual practice, helping to focus the mind and purify the soul, but also as sacred elements in home decor, bringing peace and harmony to your space. Each statue comes with detailed background information and placement suggestions, aiding you in understanding their cultural significance and spiritual value, making them essential companions on your spiritual journey.', 'Buddha Statues Series, Majestic Buddha Statues, Compassionate Expressions, Focus for Practice', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('22321621-9a20-4359-926b-0dfa602f2e75', '05e3d800-057d-497a-8916-e406dae5cfea', 'en-US', 'Shakyamuni Buddha Statue', 'The Shakyamuni Buddha statue series, showcasing the dignity and wisdom of the Buddha, is crafted using traditional techniques. It is suitable for meditation practice and home veneration, serving as a symbol of spiritual enlightenment and a medium for cultural heritage.', 'Shakyamuni Buddha Statue - A Symbol of Solemn Wisdom and Enlightenment', 'The Shakyamuni Buddha statue series showcases the dignity and wisdom of the Buddha. Our statues are crafted using traditional techniques, adhering to the proportions and characteristics described in Buddhist scriptures to ensure each piece complies with religious standards. Materials include brass, black sandalwood, crystal, and more. Each statue undergoes meticulous polishing and consecration to enhance its spiritual energy. The Shakyamuni Buddha statue is ideal for use as a visualization object during meditation practice, helping practitioners focus their attention, purify their minds, and elevate their awareness. Additionally, these statues make perfect choices for home altars, bringing a sacred atmosphere and cultural depth to your space. Every statue comes with detailed sutra explanations and practice guidance, assisting you in deepening your understanding of Buddhist teachings and progressing on the path to enlightenment.', 'Shakyamuni Buddha Statue, Dignified Wisdom, Meditation Practice, Home Altar Devotion', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('d5328c11-6b9a-4a21-a72b-84c79d8ca6d0', '07ae0908-da25-43cf-b1f1-82c3123b1ebe', 'en-US', 'Laughing Buddha Statue', 'The Laughing Buddha statue series, embodying the joy and prosperity of Maitreya Buddha, is crafted with rounded shapes and warm materials, bringing joyful energy to your space and serving as an ideal decorative piece to attract good fortune and prosperity.', 'Laughing Buddha Statue - A Symbol of Joy and Prosperity', 'The Laughing Buddha Statue series embodies the joy and prosperity associated with Maitreya Buddha. Our Laughing Buddha statues are crafted with rounded shapes and warm materials such as brass, ceramic, and resin, showcasing the approachable image of Maitreya Buddha with a large, accommodating belly and a constant smile. Each statue undergoes meticulous carving to ensure vivid expressions and rich details, conveying joyful energy and a positive mindset. The Laughing Buddha statue is perfect for placement in living rooms, offices, shops, and other spaces, serving as an ideal decorative piece to attract good fortune and prosperity. In Buddhist tradition, Maitreya Buddha symbolizes future enlightenment and worldly happiness. Our Laughing Buddha statues bring this spiritual essence to life, infusing your living space with positive energy and blessings.', 'Laughing Buddha Statue, Maitreya Buddha Statue, Symbol of Joy, Emblem of Prosperity', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('ea710f7a-1f32-4f42-ac30-f5bc0224cb6f', '8822a91d-d5e3-415e-b245-3725b3598b79', 'en-US', 'Guan Yin Statue', 'The Guanyin Buddha statue series, presenting the sacred image of compassion and salvation, is crafted with elegant shapes and delicate workmanship. It brings peace and protection to your practice and home, becoming a source of spiritual comfort.', 'Guan Yin Statue - A Sacred Symbol of Compassion and Salvation', 'The Guanyin Bodhisattva Statue Series presents the sacred image of compassion and salvation. Our Guanyin statues are crafted with elegant designs and meticulous techniques, using materials such as jade, ebony, crystal, bronze, and more. Each statue is carefully carved and polished to reveal a gentle countenance and compassionate gaze. In Buddhism, Guanyin Bodhisattva is revered as the embodiment of compassion, relieving suffering and answering the prayers of sentient beings. Our Guanyin statues are not only ideal for use during meditation and spiritual practice as objects of visualization to cultivate compassion and wisdom but also perfect for home altars, bringing peace and protection to your space. Each statue comes with detailed introductions to related scriptures and placement suggestions, helping you delve deeper into its spiritual significance and cultural value, making it an important symbol of emotional comfort and spiritual support.', 'Guan Yin Statue, Compassionate Salvation, Serene Protection, Exquisite Carving', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415', '2025-06-11 05:30:46.769415');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('677d31b8-9f6b-445e-8e6a-7f441955e9bd', 'be178bf7-c03b-48d8-9602-05b906ea6cba', 'en-US', 'Elephant God Statue', 'The elephant god statue series showcases the wisdom and power of Ganesha, the elephant-headed deity, crafted with traditional shapes and high-quality materials. It helps remove obstacles, bringing good luck and success to your life and practice.', 'Ganesh Statue - The Obstacle Remover of Wisdom and Strength', 'The Ganesha Statue Series showcases the wisdom and power of Lord Ganesha, the revered elephant-headed deity. Our Ganesha statues are crafted using traditional designs and high-quality materials such as brass, ebony, and resin. Each statue undergoes meticulous carving to highlight the distinct features of Ganesha: an elephant head on a human body, a large belly, multiple arms, and various ritual objects in hand. In Hindu tradition, Ganesha is worshipped as the god of wisdom and success, known for removing obstacles and bringing good fortune. Our Ganesha statues are perfect for placement at entrances, desks, or meditation spaces, serving as sacred symbols to clear barriers and open pathways to success. Each statue comes with detailed mythological background and blessing methods, helping you connect with ancient wisdom and infuse your life and practice with positive energy and protective strength.', 'Elephant God, Ganesha, Wisdom Power, Obstacle Remover', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('8e8fba71-af0a-4fc9-bff5-fe4a2e49b02a', '648bd9e4-f161-4b86-9aaa-46a9486d5acf', 'en-US', 'Meditation Yoga Buddha Statue', 'The Meditation Yoga Buddha Statues collection showcases the meditative postures and yoga spirit of Buddhas and Bodhisattvas, crafted with stable forms and harmonious proportions. It brings a focused energy to your practice space, making it an ideal companion for your spiritual journey.', 'Meditation Yoga Buddha Statues - A Companion for Focused Energy Practice', 'The Meditation Yoga Buddha Statues collection showcases the meditative postures and yoga spirit of Buddhas and Bodhisattvas. Our statues are crafted with stable forms and harmonious proportions, available in various materials such as brass, black sandalwood, ceramic, and more. Each statue is intricately carved to display a serene sitting posture and focused expression. Designed specifically for meditation and yoga practice spaces, these statues help create a tranquil atmosphere and enhance spiritual energy. The stable design symbolizes inner peace and concentration, making them perfect for placement in meditation corners, beside yoga mats, or in quiet study areas. Each statue comes with detailed guidance on spiritual practices and space arrangement suggestions, assisting you in creating an ideal practice environment. They will become loyal companions for your daily practice and self-exploration, guiding you toward inner balance and awakening.', 'Meditation Yoga Buddha Statues, Focus Energy, Practice Companion, Stable Design', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('bf09b552-92ac-4c7e-a5a9-dd59fee0a5f2', 'ae6c4361-2f5f-4133-80bb-a7c1fcb70588', 'en-US', 'Home Decor Catalog', 'A carefully selected category of home decor and personal items, including incense burners, keychains, ornaments, Zen gardens, and more products that combine utility and aesthetics, adding harmony and personality to your living space.', 'Home Decor Category - A harmonious and aesthetically pleasing choice for living', 'A carefully selected category of home decor and personal items, including incense burners, keychains, ornaments, Zen gardens, and more products that combine functionality with aesthetics. Our products are thoughtfully chosen, blending traditional craftsmanship with modern design to showcase unique styles and exceptional quality. Incense burners help purify the air and create a meditative atmosphere; keychains and car hangings add daily convenience and personal expression; ornaments enhance spatial beauty; and Zen gardens provide a miniature focus for meditation. Each item pays attention to detail, ensuring a superior user experience, adding harmony and personality to your living space, and serving as a bridge between material comfort and spiritual tranquility.', 'Home Decor, Incense Burner, Decorative Items, Zen Garden', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('9240f6fd-e7bb-48c7-a26e-c83c20b91ba8', 'ef5e5203-97df-468d-bfa0-2a3d64f4c1ca', 'en-US', 'Incense Burners & Incense', 'The diffuser and incense series features high-quality materials used in crafting the diffusers, paired with natural incense to help purify the space, elevate consciousness, and create an ideal atmosphere for meditation and daily life, showcasing the power of olfactory healing.', 'Incense Burners & Scents - Olfactory Healing for Space Purification', 'The incense burner and fragrance series features high-quality materials such as ceramics, metal, and stone for crafting exquisite incense burners, paired with natural plant-based fragrances. Our incense burners are designed beautifully, practical, and durable, while our fragrance selection is extensive, including traditional recipes like agarwood, sandalwood, and Tibetan incense. The smoke and aroma produced by burning the fragrances can purify the space, elevate awareness, relieve stress, and promote relaxation, making them ideal companions for activities like meditation, yoga, and reading. In many cultures, incense is seen as a bridge connecting the material world with the spiritual realm. Our products bring this ancient wisdom into modern life, helping you create a harmonious and peaceful atmosphere to enhance your daily living experience. Each incense set comes with a user guide and fragrance pairing suggestions to ensure you enjoy the best olfactory healing experience possible.', 'Incense burner, natural incense, space purification, olfactory healing', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('bff6de49-ae73-480c-b3cf-1bc84693683b', 'c939f87d-6cd9-405a-9e7f-8b74ae1e2797', 'en-US', 'Keychains + Car Hangings', 'The keychain and car hanging series, integrating practical functions with personalized design, are made of high-quality materials, showcasing a fashionable style and cultural elements, adding convenience and spiritual protection to daily travel.', 'Keychains & Car Hangs - Practical and Personalized Companions', 'The keychain and car hanging series combines practical functions with personalized designs. Our products are made of various materials such as metal, leather, gems, and Buddha statues, ensuring durability and aesthetics. The design styles range from simple and modern to religious and cultural, meeting the needs of different personalities. Keychains help organize keys and prevent loss, while car hangings add personalized decorations and spiritual protection to your beloved car. Many styles incorporate cultural elements like Buddhism and Hinduism, including Buddha statues, the six-word mantra, auspicious patterns, etc., symbolizing safety, wisdom, and good luck. These small items are not only daily necessities but also become a means of expressing spiritual beliefs, bringing convenience and positive energy to your travels, becoming a thoughtful companion and cultural messenger in your life.', 'Keychains, Car Hanging Decorations, Personalized Design, Spiritual Guardianship', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('23ea3822-69e6-4cfa-870d-ca0895e13708', '7604d919-b3dc-491f-bf9c-89d6657e7cd1', 'en-US', 'Decorative items', 'The home decor series includes items such as figurines, wall hangings, and storage products, crafted from a variety of materials and design styles to add beauty and personality to your living space, creating a harmonious and comfortable living environment.', 'Home Decor Items - The Perfect Combination of Aesthetics and Utility', 'Home decor series, including a variety of types such as figurines, wall hangings, and storage items. Our products are made from multiple materials like ceramics, wood, metal, and glass, with design styles ranging from modern minimalism to ethnic traditions, catering to different home decoration needs. Decorative items not only enhance the spatial aesthetics but also emphasize practical functions, such as figurines with storage space, adjustable wall hangings, and trays that combine decoration with functionality. Each piece is carefully designed and crafted to ensure excellent quality and perfect details. Placing appropriate decorative items can reflect the personality and taste of the residents, adding harmonious energy to the living environment and creating a comfortable and pleasant living atmosphere. Our decor series helps you create a unique and stylish living space, achieving the perfect combination of aesthetics and utility.', 'Home decor, display and hanging ornaments, practical functionality, aesthetic style', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('ae850fa9-ee5b-48ca-bacc-8153f9c6fbf7', '5894bde9-4f8b-48d7-871f-94e3d4e9641b', 'en-US', 'Meditation Zen Garden', 'The Mini Zen Garden series creates meditation focal points through elements such as sand, small sculptures, and plants, cultivating focus and patience while showcasing Japanese Zen aesthetics, adding tranquility and a meditative atmosphere to indoor spaces.', 'Meditation Zen Garden - Indoor meditation tools inspired by Japanese Zen aesthetics', 'The Mini Zen Garden series creates meditation focal points using elements such as sand, small sculptures, and plants. Our Zen gardens are exquisitely designed, crafted with high-quality materials like ceramic pots, natural sand and stones, small Buddha statues, and potted plants, showcasing the essential aesthetics of Japanese Zen Buddhism. By combining minimalist design with natural elements, these Zen gardens help cultivate focus and patience, making them ideal tools for meditation. When using a Zen garden, you can enter a state of deep relaxation through interactive activities such as raking the sand or arranging small landscapes, experiencing the tranquility and wisdom of Zen practice. These Zen gardens are perfect for placement on desks, windowsills, or side tables, adding a peaceful atmosphere to indoor spaces and becoming an important part of daily meditation and spiritual cultivation. They connect nature with inner calmness, revealing the unique charm of Eastern aesthetics.', 'Zen garden, Zen aesthetics, meditation focus, Japanese culture', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('afadba7b-b33d-4fa9-8fb1-3ad3967f1be6', 'a02c92e7-45c0-4543-abbb-3d20ca466f41', 'en-US', 'Cute Animal Decor', 'The cute animal-shaped decor series is made of materials such as resin and ceramics, showcasing the agility and fun of animals, adding a lively atmosphere to the home, and becoming an ideal decorative choice for expressing individuality and love.', 'Cute Animal Decor - Lively and Fun Personal Expression', 'The adorable animal-shaped decor series is made from various materials such as resin, ceramics, and plush. Our products capture the vitality and charm of animals, with lifelike depictions of cats, dogs, rabbits, foxes, and more, featuring rich expressions. The design styles range from realistic to cartoonish, catering to different aesthetic preferences. These decorations are perfect for living rooms, bedrooms, children''s rooms, offices, and other spaces, adding a lively atmosphere and warmth to any environment. Adorable animal decor is not just home accessories but also a way to express emotions, evoking people''s love for nature and life. Each piece is carefully crafted to ensure safety, non-toxicity, and excellent texture, making them ideal choices for expressing individuality and affection. They are especially suitable as gifts for animal lovers and children, bringing joy and warmth to everyday life.', 'Animal decorations, cute shapes, lively atmosphere, personal expression', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('543bd3bb-eba6-4419-8603-797807adde92', 'df2e0873-6539-47e8-9c4d-61c342204336', 'en-US', 'Bagua Diagram', 'The Feng Shui Bagua Chart series, designed with traditional symbols and colors, assists in the flow of energy and spatial arrangement, bringing harmony and balance to home and work environments, showcasing the applied wisdom of Feng Shui culture.', 'Feng Shui Bagua Map - A Guide to the Flow of Energy in Space', 'The Feng Shui Bagua series is designed and produced using traditional symbols and colors. Our Bagua charts are crafted from high-quality materials such as silk, paper, and acrylic, fully displaying the complete Bagua symbols and Nine Palaces grid layout. Some products also incorporate elements like zodiac signs and constellations to enhance their feng shui applications. In feng shui practice, the Bagua chart is used to analyze energy flow and guide spatial arrangements, helping to balance energy fields and improve fortune. Our Bagua charts come in various sizes and styles, suitable for hanging in important locations such as living rooms, offices, and entrance halls. Each chart includes a detailed user guide and explanation of feng shui principles, assisting you in correctly applying this ancient wisdom to bring harmony and balance to your home and workspace, serving as a practical tool that connects traditional culture with modern life.', 'Feng Shui Bagua Map, Energy Flow, Spatial Layout, Feng Shui Culture', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
INSERT INTO "public"."product_category_translations" VALUES ('013e285d-d312-4099-8708-c14ab743f858', '34dde886-3bee-402f-8f99-652d14634800', 'en-US', 'Teacup', 'An exquisite series of teacups, crafted from high-quality materials such as fine ceramics and purple clay, showcasing traditional craftsmanship and cultural significance. They provide an enjoyable experience for tea-tasting moments and are ideal utensils for both the tea ceremony and everyday use.', 'Elegant Teacup - Enjoy Tea with Traditional Craftsmanship', 'Our exquisite teacup series is crafted from high-quality materials such as premium ceramics, purple clay, and glass. Our teacups showcase the finest traditional craftsmanship, from hand-thrown shaping, carving to glaze painting, with every step meticulously controlled. The design styles range from minimalist modern, classic blue and white porcelain, Japanese Zen style, to elegant Chinese aesthetics, catering to various cultural backgrounds and aesthetic preferences. While emphasizing visual appeal, our teacups also prioritize functionality, including a comfortable grip, appropriate capacity, and superior material quality that ensures the purity of tea aroma. Using an exquisite teacup during tea tasting not only enhances the drinking experience but also becomes an essential part of cultural exchange and spiritual enjoyment. Our teacups are perfect for tea ceremony enthusiasts, collectors, and those who pursue a high-quality lifestyle, adding both traditional charm and modern elegance to your tea-tasting moments.', 'Elegant teacup, traditional craftsmanship, tea tasting experience, tea ceremony utensils', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397', '2025-06-11 05:33:02.322397');
